item.title: Some stuff wrong with my models?
item.dc:creator: @the_elve_age the elve age
item.description:
@the_elve_age wrote:

Fat Cookies:

Add animation to your models when converting them in DatMaker and make sure the model zoom is correct.

lol, animation is not weather your models show on inv models or not. its purely a recolor.

[quote=“cocoa, post:3, topic:272857”]1. Check zooms, rotations, drop model.
2. You have it set to platebody serverside. Just make it body.
3. You didn’t add model.[/quote]

Thanks cocoa, lol and number 3 was probably a retard of myself =)
